      <title>投资者押注法国资产在大选后将面临数月波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/french-election-turmoil-to-have-prolonged-impact-on-stock-and-bond-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[无论哪个政党在周日的法国议会选举中获胜，一些投资者都押注，这次选举结果将标志着该国股票和债券市场进入一个更加动荡的时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/french-election-turmoil-to-have-prolonged-impact-on-stock-and-bond-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
