    <item>
      <title>尽管股市创下历史新高，比特币仍跌至 2 月以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币连续第四个交易日下跌，这是加密货币更大范围抛售的一部分，与近期全球股市创下的历史新高形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行准备通过各大银行发行数十亿元人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行采取了进一步措施，通过出售国债来冷却创纪录的股市上涨，并表示目前通过与贷款机构达成的协议，央行可以持有“数千亿元”人民币的国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大批准嘉能可煤炭交易，泰克计划回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大已批准嘉能可公司（Glencore Plc）以 69 亿美元收购泰克资源有限公司（Teck Resources Ltd.）的冶金煤业务，后者宣布回购 20 亿美元股票并承诺提高铜产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:38:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
